                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>No record of this conversation was made by Roosevelt. Soong’s report on the
                    meeting is contained in his letter of May 18, 1943, to <pb facs="0211" n="109"
                        xml:id="pg_109"/> Roosevelt, <hi rend="italic">post</hi>, <ref
                        target="#pg_296">p. 296</ref>. The information set forth above respecting
                    the place and time of the meeting is derived from, the President’s Appointment
                    Calendar (Roosevelt Papers).</p>
            </div>
